Localhost Installation Instructions:

'>' indicates terminal input

1. Install Scala
> sudo apt-get install scala

2. Install Play
	Go to http://www.playframework.com/download and download 2.1.0 or later
	Unzip to a convenient location

3. Install Mongo
	>sudo apt-get install mongodb

4. 'cd' to app directory

5. >/play_directory/play run

6. Enter "localhost:9000" in a browser address bar